            Bazinga<br />Blue
          </h2>

          <div
            class="flex gap-4 md:block transition-opacity duration-700 peer-checked/orange:md:opacity-0 peer-checked/orange:md:pointer-events-none order-1 md:order-none"
          >
            <div class="md:mb-6">
              <div
